This mod creates unique radio stations for most factions located within the Zone.
At the moment the current faction radio stations include:

* Mercenary Base – Dead City
* Freedom Base – Yanov Station
* Freedom Base – Army Warehouse
* Duty Megaphones – Rostok
* 100 Rads Bar – Rostok
* Sid’s Bunker - Cordon
* Bandit Stronghold – Dark Valley
* Forester’s Lodge – Red Forrest
* Clear Sky’s Base – Great Swamp
* Military Base – Agraprom
* Skadovsk Ship - Zaton
* Ecologist's Bunker - Yantar
* Monolith Base - Pripyat
* Bandit's Hangar - Garbage

If you want to alter or delete the playlist, simply follow the location of the sound files for each faction and rename the .ogg files to replace the ones already there.
Don’t forget to edit this LTX file to match the same number of files in each edited group (eg: if you create 100 .ogg files for the Clear Sky base, you must name each file like this ---> anomaly_radio_addon\clear_sky_radio\ClearSky_radio_NUMBER OF FILE)

